Repost @leannalinswonderland ♥️ 🐍💞🦊 Work in progress by @lizclimo for #togetherwegrowartshow curated by @madebyboredinc ⭐️
⁠
Liz did 2 sweet and comical hand drawings for this show for the first time and we are excited to reveal them both fully this Sat., Sept. 11th! A portion of the sales will be donated to @theconsciouskid 🌈.
⁠
🥳 Join us on the opening day In-Person (12-6pm) or here on IG Live (6pm pst). All art goes online at 7pm pst!⁠
⁠
For more details slide 👈 and visit profile link 👆

Also 🙌 SAVE THE DATE: Friday, Sept. 24th @ 5pm pst for our exclusive Liz Climo signing of Best Bear plush, books, and stationery on the @popshoplive app. More details coming next week ⚡️⚡️⚡️.

node.text: A bear plushie update, as promised! We’ve heard that the plushies are now scheduled to arrive in the warehouse the 1st week of September, and will be distributed to customers the 2nd and 3rd week of September. There have been some shipping delays overseas, unfortunately, which is why they’re arriving a little later than they’d planned - but they’re coming! If anyone needs additional support, or if you have any questions at all about your order,  please contact: support@snapcreative.com 🐻♥️ Thanks again, everyone!
